data.description: Welcome Home to this Charming Updated Home, conveniently located in the NE Tacoma Neighborhood of Browns Point! This inviting home features 1-story living with 3 bedrooms + 1 full bathroom, Cozy Wood-burning Fireplace, a large level Fully-Fenced lot & updates throughout. The Kitchen boasts Quartz Counters & Stainless Steel Appliances that all stay, along with the Washer & Dryer, truly making this home turn-key and ready for the new homeowners. The Updated Bathroom includes a tile-surround shower and a door that also connects it to the Primary bedroom for convenience and ease. New Exterior Paint in 2023 and upgraded Insulation throughout the Attic and Garage. Ask about the 2.65% assumable rate and Seller Credit with the right offer!
